              "rowId": 141,
              "keyParts": [
                141,
                "p7",
                "verse",
                "v30",
                "content"
              ],
              "value": "“Now therefore, as soon as I come to your servant my father, and the boy is not with us, then, as his life is bound up in the boy’s life,"
